Willie Mae LANE, v. E. G. FITZGERALD. No. 6637. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Jan. 10, 1961. George & George, Ardmore, Okl., for appellant. W. J. Williams, Ardmore, Okl., for ap-pellee.

Before MURRAH, Chief Judge, and PICKETT and BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Docketed and dismissed on motion of appellee, counsel for appellant consenting thereto.
